\fs20 \cf4 \super \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 [3]}} According to Sankrityayan and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Dvijram_Yadav&action=edit&redlink=1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 Dvijram Yadav}}, Saraha was born in Raggyee village of ancient {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhagalpur"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 Bhagalpur}}, the then Capital of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anga_Desh"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 Anga Desh}}.{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saraha#cite_note-4"}}{\fldrslt 
